{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make socio-economic status a protected characteristic",
        "additional_details": "Better protections need to be in place to focus on addressing socio-economic inequalities.\r\n \r\nThe government needs to add socio-economic status to the Equality Act, making direct and indirect discrimination based on class or social status illegal.\r\n \r\nThis will require that socio-economic status be clearly defined, so organisations and institutions can measure it affectively.",
        "background": "The outcome of Ofqual\u2019s formula for calculating A-level results caused widespread outrage due to it disproportionately reducing the grades of students from lower socio-economic backgrounds.",
